          <p>The Twins – Curious, expressive, and full of energy. Geminis are quick thinkers who enjoy engaging in conversation and exploring new ideas. They often have a playful side and love trying new experiences that stimulate their minds. Adaptable and versatile, Geminis can easily shift between different interests and social circles.</p>
